      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4851 - Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Abi Nasr Al-Bazanti narrated from Abdul Karim ibn Amr, from Abu Basir, from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"Lian (the mutual curse between spouses) does not take place unless the man has consummated the marriage with his wife.\""
